                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6514" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0624</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8055 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“市场带技术”道路能否让自主CPU龙芯逆袭？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Loongson: Can “market with technology&quot; make it counterattack?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑刚，邓宛如</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙芯中科技术股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙芯；创新战略；关键核心技术；市场带技术；自主创新；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">oongson; Innovation strategy; Key core technology; Market with technology; Disruptive innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，美国对华科技企业的种种遏制事件表明，发展关键核心技术是强国之道，关键核心技术受制于人是国家安全的最大隐患。本案例以胡伟武为首的中科院龙芯CPU团队自主创新发展历程为主线，详细阐述了龙芯团队在“夹缝中”努力突破芯片关键核心技术的过程。不同于我国汽车等产业传统的“市场换技术”战略，龙芯在实践中摸索出了“市场带技术”的创新战略，即充分发挥我国体制优势和市场优势，通过体制内市场引导形成技术能力带动技术进步，再参与体制外市场竞争。龙芯目前已取得阶段性成果，但仍面临残酷市场竞争和打造自主产业生态的挑战。龙芯“市场带技术”的战略和关键核心技术突破的路径对其他行业和企业探索适合自己的自主创新道路和关键核心技术突破路径有参考和探讨价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Technological progress is the fundamental motive force of the development of productivity. In 2001, to break the international chip technology monopoly, the Loongson research group was established. This case is based on the development process of independent innovation of the Loongson CPU team led by Weiwu Hu. It elaborates the process of their efforts to break through the key core technology. Unlike the traditional strategy of &quot;market for technology&quot;, &quot;market with technology&quot; strategy has been explored by the practice of Loongson. &quot;Market with technology&quot; strategy has reference value for other industries and enterprises to explore their independent innovation path and key core technology breakthrough path.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《创新与变革管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关键核心技术的内涵；关键核心技术的突破:要素与过程；技术企业的组织形态:自主开发型与技术依赖型企业；自主开发型企业的开放性；颠覆性创新理论；开放式创新理论；颠覆性创新矩阵；创新生态系统理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
